title: Get Over It | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Get Over It | Joel Osteen
description:
Don’t let one bad break keep you from becoming who God created you to be. If you’ll stay in faith, He’ll take what was meant for your harm and use it for your advantage.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
